493
00:22:06,673 --> 00:22:07,935
CHEERS.

494
00:22:12,243 --> 00:22:13,201
EXCUSE ME.

495
00:22:13,984 --> 00:22:15,334
YOO-HOO.

496
00:22:17,336 --> 00:22:19,642
