BOTH YOUR LEGS?

508
00:22:36,485 --> 00:22:37,617
[WHIMPERS]

509
00:22:48,497 --> 00:22:49,759
OH, COME ON!
THIS ISN'T ROCK'N'ROLL.

510
00:22:57,898 --> 00:22:59,247
WHAT DO YOU
SMELL LIKE?

511
00:23:00,379 --> 00:23:02,163
UH...
[SNIFFS]

512
00:23:02,206 --> 00:23:03,599
OH, COME ON,
SINCE WHEN DOES A MAN

513
00:23:03,643 --> 00:23:05,166
NEED TO SHOWER
TO BE ROCK AND ROLL, EH?

514
00:23:06,559 --> 00:23:07,908
YOU SMELL LIKE DEATH.

515
00:23:08,865 --> 00:23:10,301
YOU ARE NOT EXACTLY
A BOUQUET

516
00:23:10,345 --> 00:23:12,129
OF FUCKING ROSES
EITHER, LOVE, ALL RIGHT?

517
00:23:15,481 --> 00:23:18,135
[FANS CHEERING]

518
00:23:25,316 --> 00:23:26,579
OH, FUCK OFF.

519
00:23:29,538 --> 00:23:30,887
HAVE A GOOD EVENING, SIR.

520
00:23:30,931 --> 00:23:32,019
HUH?

521
00:23:34,369 --> 00:23:35,414
SWEET!

522
00:23:45,511 --> 00:23:47,382
OH, MAMA, I'M HOME.

523
00:23:48,775 --> 00:23:50,254
COME ON.

524
00:23:50,298 --> 00:23:51,908
BANDAR WANTS
TO MEET YOU.

525
00:23:51,952 --> 00:23:52,996
WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

526
00:23:53,040 --> 00:23:54,781
MASON.

527
00:23:54,824 --> 00:23:57,131
WHEN KYLE USED TO PLAY,

528
00:23:57,174 --> 00:23:59,786
IT WAS LIKE...
A HAPPENING, YOU KNOW?

529
00:23:59,829 --> 00:24:02,789
NONE OF THIS
MANUFACTURED CRAP.

530
00:24:02,832 --> 00:24:05,835
WHEREVER HE PLAYED,
PEOPLE WOULD JUST
HEAR ABOUT IT AND COME,

531
00:24:05,879 --> 00:24:07,054
YOU KNOW
WHAT I'M SAYING?

532
00:24:07,097 --> 00:24:08,664
SURE.

533
00:24:08,708 --> 00:24:10,666
WELL, IT'S NOT
LIKE THAT ANYMORE.

534
00:24:10,710 --> 00:24:12,189
