ALL ABOUT ROCK.

535
00:24:12,233 --> 00:24:14,017
NOW IT'S ALL ABOUT
THE ROCK STAR.

536
00:24:14,061 --> 00:24:17,194
YEAH, UM, CAN YOU
INTRODUCE ME NOW?

537
00:24:17,238 --> 00:24:19,632
MM, I THINK THERE'RE
A FEW OTHER PEOPLE

538
