EFFORTLESS COOL LOOK.

545
00:24:34,168 --> 00:24:36,953
ALTHOUGH, YOU COULD USE
A LITTLE LIP GLOSS.

546
00:24:39,216 --> 00:24:40,391
DO ME.

547
00:24:45,875 --> 00:24:47,486
YEAH, YOU WISH, DUDE.

548
00:24:49,575 --> 00:24:50,793
WHAT THE HELL
DO THEY THINK?

549
00:24:51,881 --> 00:24:53,013
LET'S GO CHECK OUT
THE BUFFET.

550
00:24:53,056 --> 00:24:53,970
OKAY.

551
00:24:56,799 --> 00:25:00,194
