A VERY PROMISING CAREER

553
00:25:02,936 --> 00:25:04,415
ON THE SILVER SCREEN.

554
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:08,985
SO NOW I STAY HERE,
AND I HELP OTHER PEOPLE GO.

555
00:25:10,334 --> 00:25:12,075
AND THEY DO GO
SOMEWHERE,

556
00:25:12,119 --> 00:25:13,337
I KNOW THAT MUCH.

557
00:25:18,734 --> 00:25:21,041
I DON'T KNOW
IF THERE'S A HEAVEN OR A HELL,

558
00:25:22,608 --> 00:25:25,480
BUT I BELIEVE THERE'S MORE.

559
00:25:28,004 --> 00:25:29,353
MY WHOLE LIFE...

560
00:25:29,397 --> 00:25:31,225
MY WHOLE DEATH,

561
00:25:31,268 --> 00:25:33,532
SHOWS ME THAT THERE'S MORE.

562
00:25:34,402 --> 00:25:35,925
