563
00:25:37,536 --> 00:25:38,362
THANK YOU.

564
00:25:44,760 --> 00:25:46,066
YOU CAN'T TELL ANYONE.

565
00:25:46,762 --> 00:25:48,677
I...
[SNIFFS]

566
00:25:48,721 --> 00:25:50,026
I HAVE TO,
I HAVE TO TELL THEM.

567
00:25:51,419 --> 00:25:52,420
YEAH.

568
00:25:53,639 --> 00:25:54,944
I KNOW YOU DO.

569
00:26:05,738 --> 00:26:07,566
THANK YOU FOR GIVING ME BACK
MY FAITH.

570
00:26:18,577 --> 00:26:19,752
SO...

571
00:26:20,448 --> 00:26:22,232
IS IT TRUE?

572
00:26:22,276 --> 00:26:24,365
I DON'T KNOW WHAT THE HELL
SHE'S TALKING ABOUT, BAND-AID,

573
00:26:24,408 --> 00:26:26,759
BUT I DO WANT
A BIT MORE TEQUILA.
DO YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

574
00:26:26,802 --> 00:26:28,543
IT'S BANDAR,
MOTHERFUCKER.

575
00:26:28,587 --> 00:26:30,937
LOOK INTO HIS EYES.
HE'S DEAD.

576
00:26:31,894 --> 00:26:33,461
YOU'RE DEAD, RIGHT?

577
00:26:33,504 --> 00:26:35,463
NO, MAN, I'M DEATHLY
ATTRACTED TO YOU.

578
00:26:35,506 --> 00:26:36,943
I'M DEAD ON ARRIVAL
AT YOUR DOORSTEP.

579
00:26:36,986 --> 00:26:38,205
I'M DEAD SERIOUS.

580
00:26:40,511 --> 00:26:41,643
DON'T YOU GET IT?

581
00:26:41,687 --> 00:26:42,862
YOU'RE WITH FRIENDS NOW.

582
00:26:42,905 --> 00:26:44,298
JUST ANSWER THE QUESTION.

583
00:26:46,126 --> 00:26:47,040
ARE YOU DEAD?

584
00:26:48,824 --> 00:26:49,825
I WAS DEAD.

585
00:26:51,610 --> 00:26:53,133
AND NOW I'M NOT.

586
00:26:54,395 --> 00:26:55,744
I'M A GRIM REAPER.

587
00:26:58,225 --> 00:27:00,096
I TAKE PEOPLE'S SOULS
BEFORE THEY DIE.

588
00:27:01,576 --> 00:27:03,230
I KNEW IT.

589
00:27:03,273 --> 00:27:04,884
WHAT IS IT LIKE
TO TAKE SOMEONE'S SOUL?

590
00:27:07,364 --> 00:27:08,452
ALL RIGHT, BANDAR,

591
00:27:08,496 --> 00:27:10,193
YOU KNOW WHEN
YOU'RE PISS DRUNK,

592
00:27:11,194 --> 00:27:13,109
AND YOU COLLAPSE
ON THE FLOOR,

593
00:27:13,153 --> 00:27:14,894
AND SOMEONE COMES
TO WAKE YOU UP

594
00:27:14,937 --> 00:27:16,547
BECAUSE THE POLICE ARE
JUST ABOUT TO ARRIVE, YEAH?

595
00:27:17,374 --> 00:27:18,549
WELL, I'M THAT SOMEONE.

596
00:27:19,768 --> 00:27:21,117
AND AT FIRST,

597
00:27:22,423 --> 00:27:23,772
THEY DON'T KNOW
WHERE THEY ARE

598
00:27:23,816 --> 00:27:25,034
OR WHO THEY ARE,

599
00:27:25,078 --> 00:27:27,428
AND THEY'RE
A LITTLE BIT CONFUSED.

600
00:27:27,471 --> 00:27:28,734
WELL, THAT'S WHY
I'M THERE,

601
00:27:28,777 --> 00:27:29,952
'CAUSE I'M THERE TO...

602
00:27:30,866 --> 00:27:32,302
I'M THERE
TO REASSURE THEM.

603
00:27:32,346 --> 00:27:34,696
I'M THERE
TO MAKE THEM BELIEVE

604
00:27:34,740 --> 00:27:36,219
EVERYTHING'S ALL RIGHT.

605
00:27:38,613 --> 00:27:39,658
TO DEATH.

606
00:27:42,095 --> 00:27:43,705
AH... NICE.

607
00:27:43,749 --> 00:27:44,619
TO DEATH.

608
00:27:44,663 --> 00:27:46,186
TONIGHT.

609
00:27:52,627 --> 00:27:53,976
THANK YOU.

610
00:27:55,108 --> 00:27:56,762
THANK YOU!

611
00:27:56,805 --> 00:27:58,589
THANK YOU. THANK YOU.

612
00:27:58,633 --> 00:28:00,896
THANK YOU! THANK YOU!
THANK YOU!

613
00:28:00,940 --> 00:28:02,855
[GIGGLING]

614
00:28:03,769 --> 00:28:04,726
WHO'S THERE?

615
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:07,511
TOMMY RYAN,

616
00:28:07,555 --> 00:28:09,775
IF THAT'S YOU MAKING OUT
WITH CINDY STEVENS AGAIN
IN MY CONFESSIONAL,

617
00:28:09,818 --> 00:28:12,299
THERE'LL BE HELL TO PAY!

618
00:28:12,342 --> 00:28:15,258
[GIRL] CINDY STEVENS?
YOU ASSHOLE!

619
00:28:19,132 --> 00:28:21,264
AFTERNOON.

620
00:28:21,308 --> 00:28:22,962
UH, WE WERE--
WE WERE JUST--

621
00:28:23,005 --> 00:28:25,312
DON'T LIE, TOMMY.
NOT ON THIS DAY.

622
00:28:25,355 --> 00:28:26,748
THIS IS A HOLY DAY,

623
00:28:26,792 --> 00:28:29,490
FOR I HAVE SEEN
SOMETHING WONDERFUL.

624
00:28:29,533 --> 00:28:31,579
NOW, FALL TO YOUR KNEES
AND ASK FOR HIS FORGIVENESS.

625
00:28:31,622 --> 00:28:32,928
JESUS, FATHER!

626
00:28:32,972 --> 00:28:35,104
DO NOT USE HIS NAME IN VAIN!

627
00:28:35,148 --> 00:28:37,019
FOR HE IS REAL!

628
00:28:37,063 --> 00:28:38,978
CHILL, FATHER.
YOU'RE FREAKING ME OUT.

629
00:28:39,021 --> 00:28:40,327
WAIT!

630
00:28:40,806 --> 00:28:41,981
LISTEN TO ME,

631
00:28:42,024 --> 00:28:44,026
I HAVE SEEN
SOMETHING WONDERFUL!

632
00:28:44,070 --> 00:28:45,767
TOMMY! NO, WAIT!

633
00:28:45,811 --> 00:28:47,421
WAIT! TOMMY!
NO, WAIT! WAIT!

634
00:28:47,464 --> 00:28:48,204
WAIT, I--

635
00:28:54,950 --> 00:28:56,386
[GURGLING]

636
00:29:03,698 --> 00:29:05,439
SO...

637
00:29:05,482 --> 00:29:06,745
IS THAT
ALL THERE IS?

638
00:29:07,484 --> 00:29:08,921
NO.

639
00:29:08,964 --> 00:29:10,400
THIS IS ONLY THE START.

640
00:29:12,272 --> 00:29:13,316
LOOK.

641
00:29:26,416 --> 00:29:28,375
FATHER?YES?

642
00:29:29,419 --> 00:29:30,725
IS IT ALL THEY SAY IT IS?

643
00:29:32,466 --> 00:29:34,294
I'M AS CURIOUS
AS YOU ARE, DAISY.

644
00:29:45,174 --> 00:29:46,828
[ROCK MUSIC PLAYING]

645
00:29:49,875 --> 00:29:52,921
<i>I KNOW THERE'S
A MUCH BETTER PLACE OUT THERE.</i>

646
00:29:52,965 --> 00:29:56,577
<i>IF I COULD ONLY FIGURE OUT
HOW TO ACCESS IT.</i>

647
00:29:56,620 --> 00:29:58,274
<i>THE BETTER PLACE OUT THERE,
IN MY MIND?</i>

648
00:29:59,493 --> 00:30:01,408
<i>IT'S THE V.I.P. ROOM.</i>

649
00:30:01,451 --> 00:30:03,236
<i>AND TONIGHT...</i>

650
00:30:03,279 --> 00:30:04,977
<i>I'M FINALLY GETTING IN.</i>

651
00:30:11,722 --> 00:30:13,115
READY TO MEET KYLE?

652
00:30:13,159 --> 00:30:15,291
READY FOR YOUR BRUSH
WITH IMMORTALITY?

653
00:30:15,335 --> 00:30:17,598
YEAH, A BRUSH
SOUNDS RIGHT ABOUT NOW.

654
00:30:17,641 --> 00:30:19,861
HEY, JEANNIE.HEY, KYLE.

655
00:30:19,905 --> 00:30:21,689
