SHE SAYS HI.

656
00:30:21,732 --> 00:30:23,169
OH. THANKS.

657
00:30:23,212 --> 00:30:24,823
UM, THIS IS GEORGE.

658
00:30:24,866 --> 00:30:26,476
SHE'S WITH THE NETWORK.

659
00:30:26,520 --> 00:30:27,869
ACTUALLY,
I'M AN INTERN.

660
00:30:27,913 --> 00:30:29,436
UH, JENNY...

661
00:30:29,479 --> 00:30:30,741
IT'S JEANNIE.

662
00:30:30,785 --> 00:30:32,091
YEAH.

663
00:30:32,134 --> 00:30:33,266
KYLE DOESN'T DO
MEET-AND-GREETS

664
00:30:33,309 --> 00:30:34,920
THIS CLOSE TO PERFORMANCE.

665
00:30:34,963 --> 00:30:36,312
PLEASE TRY
TO RESPECT THAT.

666
00:30:38,793 --> 00:30:40,316
OH...KAY.

667
00:30:40,360 --> 00:30:41,927
