ROCK-BLOCKED US.

668
00:30:41,970 --> 00:30:43,493
THAT WASN'T COOL.

669
00:30:43,537 --> 00:30:45,191
WELL, LET'S BLOW.

670
00:30:45,234 --> 00:30:46,322
I'M GOING TO
STICK AROUND AWHILE.

671
00:30:46,366 --> 00:30:48,150
HE'S NOT REALLY
IMMORTAL, YOU KNOW.

672
00:30:48,194 --> 00:30:49,630
YOU CAN TOUCH HIM,

673
00:30:49,673 --> 00:30:51,501
BUT NOTHING'S GOING
TO BRUSH OFF ON YOU.

674
00:30:53,242 --> 00:30:55,462
<i>IT'S ONE THING TO SHOW UP,
TAKE A SOUL,</i>

675
00:30:55,505 --> 00:30:57,725
<i>GET ON WITH YOUR AFTERLIFE.</i>

676
00:30:57,768 --> 00:31:00,859
<i>YOU CAN THINK OF YOURSELF
LIKE SOME KIND OF...</i>

677
00:31:00,902 --> 00:31:02,730
<i>ACCIDENT.</i>

678
00:31:02,773 --> 00:31:04,123
<i>BUT WHEN YOU HAVE TO
WORK AT IT,</i>

679
00:31:04,166 --> 00:31:07,169
<i>IT FEELS MORE LIKE... MURDER.</i>

680
00:31:33,282 --> 00:31:34,501
