681
00:31:37,069 --> 00:31:38,940
WHY, RUBE,
IS THERE A GENTLEMAN

682
00:31:38,984 --> 00:31:40,724
LURKING UNDERNEATH
THAT COLD DEMEANOR?

683
00:31:47,122 --> 00:31:48,297
WHERE'S YOUR CROSS?

684
00:31:49,951 --> 00:31:51,300
