FOR GOD'S SAKE.

685
00:31:53,520 --> 00:31:56,958
I WANTED GOLDEN TRUMPETS
AND ANGELS SINGING.

686
00:31:57,002 --> 00:31:59,482
I JUST EXPECTED IT
TO BE FAR MORE GLAMOROUS.

687
00:32:01,789 --> 00:32:05,314
THERE'S A PLACE
IN BOMBAY.

688
00:32:07,490 --> 00:32:09,144
IT'S CALLED
THE TOWER OF SILENCE.

689
00:32:11,581 --> 00:32:12,974
WHEN SOMEBODY DIES,

690
00:32:14,149 --> 00:32:15,977
