HAVE AT IT.

694
00:32:27,032 --> 00:32:28,555
OUR ENDINGS,
DAISY...

695
00:32:29,599 --> 00:32:30,861
THEY ARE WHAT THEY ARE.

696
00:32:31,775 --> 00:32:32,863
GREAT.

697
00:32:38,434 --> 00:32:39,522
SO?

698
00:32:42,482 --> 00:32:44,223
