ON YOUR PLANET?

708
00:33:36,710 --> 00:33:39,060
IT'S A VERY BRIGHT BLUE.

709
00:33:41,236 --> 00:33:44,065
OH, I CAN'T...
I CAN'T DO THIS RIGHT NOW.

710
00:33:44,848 --> 00:33:45,719
REGGIE, LET'S GO.

711
00:33:46,937 --> 00:33:48,287
I'VE NEVER
BEEN HERE BEFORE.

712
00:33:48,330 --> 00:33:49,505
I WANT TO STAY.

713
00:33:49,549 --> 00:33:51,072
REGGIE...

714
00:33:51,116 --> 00:33:53,727
SHE'S NEVER BEEN HERE
BEFORE, JOY.

715
00:33:56,251 --> 00:33:57,252
ALL RIGHT, FINE.

716
00:33:57,818 --> 00:33:59,080
LET'S BE HERE.

